Pick up the bar of soap.

Put the bar of soap inside the sink and turn on the water, then turn off the water and remove the soap from the sink.
Turn left then walk forward and turn right to face the wire shelf.
Place the bar of soap on the shelf.

anns.task_desc: Wash the bar soap to put it in the middle metal shelf.

Wash the soap in the sink and then pick it back up.

Place the soap on the middle metal shelf.

Pick up the pink bar of soap that is on the sink.
Move around to face the front of the sink.
Rinse the bar of soap off in the sink before picking it back up.
Turn to your left and move over to the silver shelving.
Place the bar of soap on the second shelf.

Pick up the bar of soap on the sink.
Bring the bar of soap to the front of the sink.
Put the soap in the sink and turn on water, then turn the water off.
Pick up the bar of soap from the sink and brink it over to the metal shelves.
Put the soap on the second shelf from the top.
